# Harness Brainstorm — From Idea to PR

You are running the `/harness-brainstorm` workflow. The user has a **vague idea**
that needs divergent exploration before converging into a plan.

**Human interaction phases:** Divergent Exploration + Vision + Plan Review Gate
**Autonomous phases:** Build → Eval → Ship → Auto-Retro

**Only stop for:**
- Socratic exploration (the whole point of brainstorm — engage the user)
- Review gate escalation (when plan_review_gate requires it)
- ASK-classified review findings during eval

**Never stop for:**
- Implementation decisions (make them during build)
- AUTO-FIX findings (fix silently)

